OL,3,CAncient church has windows smashed in
OL,4,C'strange and sad' vandalism incident
OL,6,FAn ancient Sussex church is facing an
OL,7,F"eye-watering" repair bill costing
OL,8,Fmany thousands of pounds after almost
OL,9,Fall of its windows were vandalised.
OL,11,FAll Saints Church, a Grade I listed
OL,12,Fbuilding in Buncton, near Steyning,
OL,13,Fwas targeted at some point between
OL,14,FTuesday 13 January and Sunday 18
OL,15,FJanuary.
OL,17,FDoor handles and lights were also
OL,18,Fdamaged at the chapel, which dates
OL,19,Fback to the 11th century.
