OL,3,CAncient church has windows smashed in
OL,4,C'strange and sad' vandalism incident
OL,6,FThe incident comes at a time when the
OL,7,Fcongregation at the church was
OL,8,Fincreasing, with services now weekly
OL,9,Frather than monthly because of their
OL,10,Fpopularity.
OL,12,FThe church's rector James di
OL,13,FCastiglione said: "Someone's
OL,14,Fclearly... done quite a prolific piece
OL,15,Fof vandalism on what is a very loved
OL,16,Fplace.
OL,18,F"It's been quite a strange and sad
OL,19,Fincident.
