OL,3,CAncient church has windows smashed in
OL,4,C'strange and sad' vandalism incident
OL,6,F"We're just grappling with what lies
OL,7,Fahead of us and... the vandalism comes
OL,8,Fon top of our major restoration
OL,9,Fproject we're just embarking on, so
OL,10,Fsome of those sums are a bit eye-
OL,11,Fwatering right now, but we're just
OL,12,Fstarting to work together as the local
OL,13,Fcongregation to tackle this challenge.
OL,15,F"We've got a strong base of local
OL,16,Fsupport and we'll be looking to tackle
OL,17,Fthis together as a church family, as
OL,18,Fwe look to God to help us rebuild and
OL,19,Flook to the future."
