OL,3,CAncient church has windows smashed in
OL,4,C'strange and sad' vandalism incident
OL,6,FIn a statement, Sussex Police said:
OL,7,F"Earlier this week, a report was made
OL,8,Fto police after a number of windows
OL,9,Fwere found to have been damaged at the
OL,10,FAll Saints Church in Water Lane,
OL,11,FBuncton.
OL,13,F"It is believed that the damage
OL,14,Foccurred between Tuesday 13 January
OL,15,Fand Sunday 18 January.
OL,17,F"As enquiries take place, it's
OL,18,Fimportant that any relevant
OL,19,Finformation is reported to police.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
