OL,4,C'strange and sad' vandalism incident
OL,6,F"If you have heard anything regarding
OL,7,Fthe damage, or saw anyone acting
OL,8,Fsuspiciously near All Saints Church
OL,9,Fbetween 13`18 January, we ask that you
OL,10,Fcome forward. Any information could be
OL,11,Fhelpful.
OL,13,F"To make a report, contact police
OL,14,Fonline or by calling 101 quoting
OL,15,Freference 541 of 19/01."
